Introduction

Joo Chang Uk, better known as Changuk, is a South Korean singer under Woollim Entertainment. He made his official debut on October 28, 2020, as a member of the boy group DRIPPIN.

When he was a trainee, Changuk participated in the hit reality show Produce X 101 where he finished 29th place.
